reviewText:
The movie and the service i got from ordering from Amazon was perfect along with the price.
I will keep ording from Amazon and recommend Amazon to others.
This was recommended in a class that I took on "forgotten westerns" and I was surprised to find that I really enjoyed it, in addition to getting a look at what people watched back in that era.

This movie was an interesting movie as it was pretty much the same type of movies that the other white Cowboys made. Herb Jeffries is a good singer as well. The story was a one similiar to a John Wayne or Roy Rogers movie. I enjoyed it very much. These people did an excellent job of acting. No doubt I will be viewing it again from time to time.

I liked the movie alright, however, the quality of the film was too dark and murky.  I realize that the film, at the time it was made, it was not in the best quality.  I also understand that the movie was made in 1939.  So dismissing, the above, the film was fine.
